/* omnia/xii_admission: the EXISTING operational rule-admission decision (ADMIT iff
 * root-confluent AND terminating).  Reused -- not reinvented -- and composed below with the
 * kernel's semantic-soundness gate, because admission alone checks OPERATION, not MEANING. */
